The '''2008 Icelandic truck  driver protests''' were [[protest]]s started by [[truck driver]]s in [[Iceland]] through March−April 2008. The protest came about due to increasing [[Price of oil|oil prices]] and [[working hours]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/europe/04/24/iceland.fuel/index.html |title=Iceland fuel protests heat up |last1=Whiteman |first1=Hilary |date=24 April 2008 |website=[[CNN]] |publisher= |accessdate=24 April 2008}}</ref>

