{|{{Infobox ship begin |display title=ital}} {{Infobox ship image | Ship image=[[File:Prinses Beatrix bezoekt zeilwedstrijden op de Langweerderwielen te Langweer, de , Bestanddeelnr 910-6350.jpg|300px|De Groene Draeck at a sailing regatta, August 1959]] | Ship caption=''De Groene Draeck'' at a sailing regatta, August 1959 }} {{Infobox ship career | Hide header= | Ship country= Netherlands | Ship flag= {{Shipboxflag|Netherlands|civil}} | Ship name= ''De Groene Draeck'' | Ship namesake= | Ship owner=[[Beatrix of the Netherlands]] | Ship operator= | Ship registry=Amsterdam | Ship route= | Ship ordered= | Ship awarded= | Ship builder=G. de Vries Lentsch | Ship original cost= | Ship yard number= | Ship way number= | Ship laid down= | Ship launched=1957 | Ship sponsor= | Ship christened= | Ship completed= | Ship acquired= | Ship maiden voyage= | Ship in service= | Ship out of service= | Ship renamed= | Ship reclassified= | Ship refit= | Ship struck= | Ship reinstated= | Ship homeport= | Ship identification=VA 18 | Ship motto= | Ship fate= | Ship status= {{Ship in active service | 2016}} | Ship notes= | Ship badge= }} {{Infobox ship characteristics | Hide header= | Header caption= | Ship class= | Ship type= [[:nl:Lemsteraak|Lemsteraak]] | Ship tonnage= | Ship displacement= | Ship tons burthen= | Ship length= {{Convert|15|m|ftin|abbr=on}} [[Length between perpendiculars|p/p]] | Ship beam= {{Convert|4.7|m|ftin|abbr=on}} | Ship height= | Ship draught={{Convert|1|m|ftin|abbr=on}} | Ship depth= | Ship power= | Ship propulsion= | Ship sail plan=*[[Gaff rig]]ged *Sail area {{Convert|175|sqm|abbr=on}} | Ship speed= | Ship endurance= | Ship capacity= | Ship crew= | Ship notes= }} |} '''''De Groene Draeck''''' ([[English language|English]]: ''The Green Dragon'') is a [[royal yacht]] of [[Beatrix of the Netherlands]]. It was named after the flagship of [[Piet Pieterszoon Hein|Piet Hein]], a famous 17th century Dutch [[admiral]].
De Groene Draeck is a traditional Dutch round bottomed sailing ship, built in 1957 in [[Amsterdam]]. She was offered by the Dutch people to the then Princess Beatrix for her 18th birthday.<ref>{{nl}} [http://www.friesland-holland-nieuws.nl/rubrieken/Trad_zeilschepen.html Newspaper criticism of Royal expenditure]</ref> Her sail number is therefore VA 18.
The ship is regularly used by the Royal Family for sailing. The ship is usually moored in [[Muiden]].
